00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:47,073
Everyone in Kerning City knew JM From the Streets was loud... and most assumed that loudness meant he was wrong. He spun theories about the swamp, about the things crawling out of it... about a creature called Dyle that he INSISTED was no ordinary Ligator. The pharmacy drawers became his private relay system... numbered, positioned, never explained... and his errands traced the outline of a network he only half understood. The city's official channels ignored him. The underground tolerated him... as a useful eccentric. Nobody considered, at first... that the paranoid man on the corner had simply been paying attention.
